anism">Single-celled<br /> life</a></b></span></div> </div> <div class="bar" style="font-size:100%; background-color:#99ffff; border-style: none; position:absolute; text-align:center; margin-top:0em; height:27.753303964758em; margin-left:0.7em; width:9.3em;"> <div class="nudge" style="font-size:100%; position:relative; top:6.94em; left:0.2em;"><span style="position:relative; align:center; vertical-align:middle; bottom:-13.876651982379em;"><i><b><small><a href="/wiki/Evolution_of_photosynthesis" title="Evolution of photosynthesis"><span style="color:green;">photosynthesis</span></a></small></b></i></span></div> </div> <div class="bar" style="font-size:100%; background-color:#b3ffea; border-style: none; position:absolute; text-align:center; margin-top:0em; height:16.651982378855em; margin-left:1.4em; width:8.6em;"> <div class="nudge" style="font-size:100%; position:relative; top:5.14em; left:0em;"><span style="position:relative; align:center; vertical-align:middle; bottom:-8.3259911894273em;"><b><a href="/wiki/Eukaryote" title="Eukaryote">Eukaryotes</a></b></span></div> </div> <div class="bar" style="font-size:100%; background-color:#ccffe7; border-style: none; position:absolute; text-align:center; margin-top:0em; height:11.894273127753em; margin-left:1.4em; width:8.6em;"> <div class="nudge" style="font-size:100%; position:relative; top:-0.06em; left:0em;"><span style="position:relative; align:center; vertical-align:middle; bottom:-5.9471365638767em;"><b><a href="/wiki/Multicellular_organism" title="Multicellular organism">Multicellular<br /> life</a></b></span></div> </div> <div class="bar" style="font-size:100%; background-color:#cc9900; border-style: none; position:absolute; text-align:center; margin-top:0em; height:3.5191189427313em; margin-left:2em; width:8em;"> <div class="nudge" style="font-size:100%; position:relative; top:1.14em; left:0em;"></div> </div> <div class="bar" style="font-size:100%; background-color:; border-style: none; position:absolute; text-ali